<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to "The rhythm of the deer." A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />My God, my God, why have you abandoned me?</para>

<para style="q1">Why are you so far from saving me and far from the words of my anguish?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />My God, I cry out in the daytime, but you do not answer,</para>

<para style="q1">and at night I am not silent!</para>
